parcel.name: DAEMON Museum
parcel.description:
DAEMON museum currently has 306 works on display.


The final number on display is
3 types of Big titles and
101 different DANDELION'S-DREAM series, and
101 GRANDMA series, and
101 HOLY-FACE series.
A total of 306 works will be exhibited.

DAEMON project will continue after that, so
DAEMON Museum is planned to be expanded.

features.text: It may be necessary to reload the file after the move.

THE GREEN NIGHT
{:style="font-size:25px"}

  | English       | Japanese    |
  | ----------- |:---------:|
  | Something grows without being noticed.          | 何かが、人知れず育ってゆく。     |
  | Something is growing and reproducing.         | どんどん繁殖してゆく。  |
  | Soon, very soon, it will be fulfilled.         | もうすぐ、もうすぐ成就する。       |
 | The perfect world inside of me, so ominous, so divine.        | 禍々しく、神々しい、眼の奥の完璧な世界。       |
{:style="font-size:20px"}

SANZU RIVER
{:style="font-size:25px"}


  | English       | Japanese    |
  | ----------- |:---------:|
  | The waters of this river do not flow.          | この川の水は流れない。     |
  | The waters of this river are still.         | この川の水は静止している。  |
  | The waters of this river do not get anywhere.         | この川の水は、どこにも辿り着けない。       |
 | They stay in this river. Forever.        | この川に留まり続ける。永久に。       |
{:style="font-size:20px"}

DANDELION BUDDHA
{:style="font-size:25px"}

  | English       | Japanese    |
  | ----------- |:---------:|
  | There is no warm salvation.         | あたたかい救済はない。     |
  | There is no soft hope.         | やわらかな希望もない。  |
  | There is only transparent prayer.        | ただあるのは、透明な祈りだけ。       |
{:style="font-size:20px"}
